node.text: The Serena & Lily collection transforms Whitney Port’s backyard into her dream space.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Serena & Lily on July 23, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Ends tonight: The Pillows & Throws Sale. ✨ Sometimes it's the littlest things that make the biggest impact. #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Serena & Lily on July 22, 2021 tagging @palmbeachlately, @thecolonypalmbeach, and @brantleyphoto. May be an image of furniture and bedroom.

node.text: Your room is ready. 🗝️ Dreaming of waking up in The Sisters Suite by @palmbeachlately at @thecolonypalmbeach. 📷:@brantleyphoto #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Serena & Lily on July 22, 2021. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: Spotlight on: The Captiva Bar. 🪴Set the bar high for your outdoor gatherings. This brings texture and easy elegance to the mix. Specially crafted to capture the look of handwoven rattan, it’s made of weather-friendly resin to resist sun and rain. A true crowd pleaser, it can move around the party with ease thanks to smooth-rolling casters. With an enclosed bottom shelf, it holds barware beautifully while keeping everything in place. And, with two levels of display, we also love using it for an artful array of plants. #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Serena & Lily on July 21, 2021 tagging @lifeoncedarlane. May be an image of furniture, living room and bedroom.

node.text: @lifeoncedarlane creates the ideal summer bedroom with our light and airy Shore Bench and easy-to-layer Cambria Quilt. #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Serena & Lily on July 21, 2021. May be an image of furniture and living room.

node.text: Savor summer living. ☀️ Explore our new arrivals at the link in our profile. #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Serena & Lily on July 20, 2021 tagging @monikahibbs. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: We adore everything about this space. From the unique mix of patterns, soothing hues, and precious pup, there are so many details to love. 🐾 📷: @monikahibbs #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Serena & Lily on July 20, 2021. May be an image of sofa and living room.

node.text: Starts now: Our Pillows & Throws Sale. Enjoy special pricing (plus free shipping)*. #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Serena & Lily on July 19, 2021 tagging @chrissymarieblog. May be an image of kitchen.

node.text: We love how @chrissymarieblog elevates this coastal kitchen with our Riviera Counter Stools and Teak Step Stool. #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Serena & Lily on July 19, 2021. May be an image of furniture and living room.

node.text: Come together in comfort and style. ✨ Enjoy 20% off custom furniture with code JUSTFORYOU. #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Serena & Lily on July 18, 2021 tagging @gncgarden. May be an image of flower, tree and outdoors.

node.text: Dreaming of spending summer days surrounded by @gncgarden's blooming hydrangeas. ☀️ #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Serena & Lily on July 18, 2021. May be an image of furniture and bedroom.

node.text: Dress up your space with our painterly botanical pattern. Crafted with exceptional detail, our Elm Chair in Priano Navy Linen is our update to the classic wingback, now 20% off with code JUSTFORYOU. #serenaandlily

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Serena & Lily on July 17, 2021 tagging @peonyinteriordesigns. May be an image of table and indoor.

node.text: There are plenty of great ways to carve out a spot that's stylish and functional. We love how @peonyinteriordesigns creates an inspired workspace with our Shore Dining Chair and Del Mar Pillow. #serenaandlily
